    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>梦想的欧洲之旅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出发前往欧洲最奇妙角落的难忘旅程！这款激动人心的游戏为您提供独特机会，无需离开家门即可游览分布在15个不同国家的30个不可思议的地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的路线将穿越雄伟的国家公园、拥有世界杰作的鼓舞人心的博物馆以及保存着几个世纪秘密的古老城堡。每个新地点都是沉浸在不同文化中、享受建筑杰作和发现旧世界隐藏宝藏的机会。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索与发现</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将遇到需要全神贯注的具有挑战性的隐藏物体场景，以及考验您逻辑和智慧的巧妙迷你游戏。收拾行装，准备冒险 - 真正的欧洲之旅等待着您！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345050/extras/70a9a867e5e0423cecf930c9098cb1b4.poster.avif?t=1762775389\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345050/extras/70a9a867e5e0423cecf930c9098cb1b4.webm?t=1762775389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345050/extras/70a9a867e5e0423cecf930c9098cb1b4.mp4?t=1762775389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>典藏版特点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们为真正的旅行者准备了包含独家内容的特别版：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 8个额外可探索地点<br>• 12个奖励迷你游戏用于提升技能<br>• 带有优美原声的便捷音乐播放器<br>• 独家桌面壁纸合集<br>• 虚拟纪念品收藏以铭记您的旅程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345050/extras/20a78e917bae720fef0ecaf8dd7361c6.poster.avif?t=1762775389\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345050/extras/20a78e917bae720fef0ecaf8dd7361c6.webm?t=1762775389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345050/extras/20a78e917bae720fef0ecaf8dd7361c6.mp4?t=1762775389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发现旧世界的魔力，成为欧洲国家的真正专家！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在访问所有国家并完成纪念品收藏后，您将参加一个特别仪式，获得&quot;真正的欧洲鉴赏家&quot;称号。您将获得特别的欧洲旅行者文凭，并有权访问包含欧洲文化和地标独家材料的私人画廊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
